  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the safety and performance of the NeoChord DS1000
      Artificial Chordae Delivery System in implanting ePTFE sutures(s) as artificial neochordae in
      patients with mitral regurgitation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
